### 2-User Registration
_Request_
```
POST /api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "whatever@example.com",
  "password": "password",
  "password_confirmation": "password"
}
```
_Response_
```
status: 201
body:

{
  "data": {
    "type": "users",
    "id": "1",
    "attributes": {
      "email": "whatever@example.com",
      "api_key": "jgn983hy48thw9begh98h4539h4"
    }
  }
}
```

